high_descs: Make a right to face the kitchen island.
Pick up the large yellow knife closest to the edge of the kitchen island.
Make a right and turn another right to reach the fridge.
Slice the closest tomato with the large yellow knife.
Turn to face the fridge again.
Set the knife in the fridge.
Turn to open the fridge again.
Pick up the slice of tomato from the fridge.
Turn right to walk to the microwave.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk back to the fridge.
Put the slice of tomato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a slice of tomato in the microwave to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and step forward to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cut the tomato in the fridge into slices.
Look up to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Look up to face the fridge.
Pick up the tomato slice in the fridge.
Turn right and cross the room to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat the tomato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Move forward, then face the table in your right.
Pick up the big knife at the edge of the table.
Turn right and walk across the room, then left to the refrigerator
Move to the refrigerator and open it.
Close the refrigerator and move back a little from it.
Open the refrigerator, put the knife on the tray and close it.
Move closer to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and pick up a slice of tomato and close it.
Turn around and head to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato slice inside and turn on the microwave, then remove the tomato slice.
Turn left across the room, then face the refrigerator.
Put the cooked tomato slice in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot slice of tomato in the refrigerator.
